<P>UPON the death of George I, his &s;on George II<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1 letter"> a&s;cended the throne, of inferior abilities to th<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1 letter"> late King; and con&s;equently &s;till
