<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1 word"> increa&s;e. To pay off this,
the mini&s;try propo&s;<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1+ letters"> many
projects, and put &s;ome into execution; bu<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1 letter"> what could be expected from a &s;et of men who ma<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1+ letters"> the public wealth only &s;ub&s;ervient
to private intere&s;<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="OXF" EXTENT="1 letter"> and who grew
